  "prompt": "What is the best Android app for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics?",
  "response": "One of the best Android apps for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics is \"Musixmatch\" combined with a music streaming service like Spotify or Apple Music. Here's why:\n\n### Musixmatch\n**Key Features:**\n- **Lyrics Synchronization:** Musixmatch offers real-time synchronized lyrics for a vast library of songs.\n- **Integration:** It can integrate with popular music streaming apps like Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube, allowing you to see lyrics while listening to songs on those platforms.\n- **Offline Lyrics:** You can download lyrics for offline use.\n- **Floating Lyrics:** The app provides a floating lyrics window that can be displayed over other apps.\n\n**How to Use:**\n1. Download and install Musixmatch from the Google Play Store.\n2. Connect it to your preferred music streaming service (e.g., Spotify).\n3. Play a song on your streaming app, and Musixmatch will display the lyrics in real-time.\n\n### Spotify\n**Key Features:**\n- **Extensive Library:** Spotify has a vast collection of English songs.\n- **Offline Downloads:** You can download songs for offline listening with a Premium subscription.\n- **Lyrics Display:** Spotify has started integrating lyrics directly into the app, though it's not as comprehensive as Musixmatch.\n\n**How to Use:**\n1. Download and install Spotify from the Google Play Store.\n2. If you have a Premium account, download songs for offline listening.\n3. Use Musixmatch alongside Spotify for the best lyrics experience.\n\n### Apple Music\n**Key Features:**\n- **High-Quality Audio:** Apple Music offers high-quality streaming.\n- **Offline Downloads:** Similar to Spotify, you can download songs for offline listening with a subscription.\n- **Lyrics Integration:** Apple Music has built-in lyrics that sync with the music, though it might not cover as many songs as Musixmatch.\n\n**How to Use:**\n1. Download and install Apple Music from the Google Play Store.\n2. If you have a subscription, download songs for offline listening.\n3. Use Musixmatch alongside Apple Music for a more comprehensive lyrics experience.\n\n### Conclusion\nCombining Musixmatch with a music streaming service like Spotify or Apple Music offers the best experience for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics. Musixmatch's real-time synchronized lyrics and broad compatibility make it an excellent choice for enhancing your music listening experience on Android.",
